PersonalMission.Name: SPG-8: I Did My Best
PersonalMission.Description: You receive experience for all effective actions. Try to be the MVP: cause damage, assist in destroying enemy vehicles, and survive the battle. Change your position after every shot; otherwise, the counter fire of enemy SPGs can destroy your vehicle.

Primary.Conditions: Be among the top 7 players on your team by experience earned
